## ??? ARCHITECTURE OVERVIEW

### **Fire-and-Forget Pattern (Key Feature)**

```
User clicks Submit
       ?
API responds immediately (< 100ms)
       ?
Background task starts (3-8 seconds)
       ?
UI polls every 2 seconds
       ?
Result appears automatically
```

**Why this matters:**
- ? **Without:** User waits 3-8 seconds with frozen page
- ? **With:** Instant feedback, real-time updates, smooth UX

